<h2>Rapid Descriptions</h2>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView44' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid1963">Linville Falls</a></b> <br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Puting in at the Falls</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView165' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17579/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17579.jpg">
</a>
<i>Puting in at the Falls</i></div><div>Photo of TR by KE @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
It is possible but not recommended to put in below the falls. Be discrete and try not to cause too much erosion.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView45' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8017">Brushy Ridge Trail</a></b> <br>
Another east rim access point, this trail travels 1.7 miles down from Mtn Park road, providing a nice putin above the better part of the paddle in, while avoiding the flatter upper 2.6 miles.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView46' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid1965">Babel Tower Rapid</a></b> (Class 5.0, Mile 4.5)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Babel Tower left line</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView169' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17580/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17580.jpg">
</a>
<i>Babel Tower left line</i></div><div>Photo of KE @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
A classic putin option with a hell of a first drop. <br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView47' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid6038">Nowhere to Run</a></b> (Class 5.0, Mile 4.7)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Nowhere to Run</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView173' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17728/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17728.jpg">
</a>
<i>Nowhere to Run</i></div><div>Photo by PM @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
Stay right and keep her straight. No way around at all. A good rapid.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView48' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid6466">Nowhere to Run</a></b> (Class 5.0, Mile 4.7)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Nowhere to Run</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView177' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17728/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17728.jpg">
</a>
<i>Nowhere to Run</i></div><div>Photo by PM @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
Stay right and keep her straight. No way around at all. A good rapid.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView49' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8041">Sweet Shoulder Boof</a></b> (Class IV, Mile 5.0)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Sweet Shoulder Boof</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView181' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17729/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17729.jpg">
</a>
<i>Sweet Shoulder Boof</i></div><div>Photo of KE by PM @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
Just drive off the big shoulder on the right for a great boof. Smiles and railgrabs are a must.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView50' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid6467">Sweet Shoulder Boof</a></b> (Class IV, Mile 5.0)<br>
