</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView51' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8042">Drunk Tank</a></b> (Class 5.2, Mile 5.7)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
