<h1>Jailhouse</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView237' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17739/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17739.jpg">
</a>
<i>Jailhouse</i></div><div>Photo of Adam Griffin by PM @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
The floods of 2004 cleaned this one up a bit, lowering the pucker by filling in some voids.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView64' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid6477">Cyclops</a></b> (Class IV+, Mile 6.2)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>pool below Cyclops</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView241' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/17740/size/big/">
<img class='riverdetail' src="/photos/archive/medium/17740.jpg">
</a>
<i>pool below Cyclops</i></div><div>Photo by KE @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
A fun rapid that suprises you. You will run some boogie below jailhouse that throws you into a blind ledge. The safe line is left of center, but a sweet boof is to be had far right, just don't get pocketed.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView65' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8051">Cyclops</a></b> (Class IV+, Mile 6.2)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>pool below Cyclops</h1>
