</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView71' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8054">Clapper Falls</a></b> (Class 5.0, Mile 6.6)<br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Clapper Falls</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView261' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
