</a>
<i>Clapper Falls</i></div><div>Photo by KE @ 1.65</div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
</div> 
This big double drop is always interesting. Boof right then clap down on another drop that deposits you into an interesting hole.<br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsRiverRapidView72' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid8055">Seal Launch Portage</a></b> <br>
<div class='rapid-inline'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Seal Launch Portage</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzqasc6tpu2pgpsPhotoDetailView265' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='photo-inline'>
