<div class='commentbox'>
Wood Update from Kirk Eddlemon on 04/01/09 Still wood in China rapid above Death Penalty, where<br/>
flow goes left to right to a very blind slot, which has a sticky lateral hole at high water. Wood<br/>
across bottom. Runnable with care, but heads up rounding the corner. Tony's rapid, shortly above<br/>
jailhouse, where you run left then center, wood in left side, unrunnable. Had to portage. Cathedral<br/>
Gorge and the rest was clean. </div>
